{
  "stem": "3165.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told the Primacs, I says, I'm going now to look for my sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, well, do you know where to go?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I says, well, I'll just hitchhike and go and look for her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they wished me good luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they told me that if I found her, I can come back with her to their place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So here I went to the highway and started the hitchhiking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And sure enough, a truck stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a man and a lady, and they had a young child with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told me to jump up in the truck-- in the open truck there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told the farmer-- like, I think somebody told me where there's some Czechoslovakian farmers are like-- I can't remember how many kilometers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I don't know, but he told me how far I should go, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I told this farmer, will you stop at so and so village-- whatever I told him, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the highway, I told him, I'll let-- I'll let you know where.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or I could have told him where to stop, so I can get off and look for farmers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says, OK, he'll stop there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we're driving, and we're driving, driving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I sort of-- I thought-- like I say, I can't remember how many kilometers it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Maybe 100, 120, 130, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I thought, this should be-- he should be stopping here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's not stopping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'm knocking on the window, you know, to-- he should see me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he is driving away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He is driving away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought, oh, God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where am I going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, you missed the place already.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
